snippet.title: THE BENGAL FILES Official Trailer | Vivek Agnihotri | Abhishek A | Pallavi J | Zee Studios | 5 Sept
snippet.description:
From the makers of The Kashmir Files and The Tashkent Files, here is the official trailer of THE BENGAL FILES, the powerful conclusion to the trilogy by two-time National Award-winning filmmaker Vivek Ranjan Agnihotri.

A presentation by: Tej Narayan & Snehlatha Agarwal and I Am Buddha

Directed by: Vivek Ranjan Agnihotri
Produced by: Abhishek Agarwal, Pallavi Joshi and Vivek Ranjan Agnihotri 
Worldwide Release: Zee Studios
Music: Zee Music Co.
Starring: Mithun Chakraborty, Anupam Kher, Pallavi Joshi, Darshan Kumaar, Simratt Kaur

This September, witness the untold truth of the Hindu genocide.

#TheBengalFiles #RightToLife

snippet.title: Rao Bahadur | Teaser | Satya Dev | Venkatesh Maha | GMB | SriChakraas | A+S | Summer 2026
snippet.description:

snippet.title: BORDER 2 Official Trailer | Sunny Deol, Varun Dhawan, Diljit Dosanjh | Republic Day 2026
snippet.description:
BORDER 2 Official Trailer | Sunny Deol, Varun Dhawan, Diljit Dosanjh | Republic Day 2026

üáÆüá≥ The wait is over! Presenting the BORDER 2 (Fan-Made) Trailer ‚Äì India‚Äôs biggest war drama returns with more power, more patriotism, and more emotion than ever before.

This video is made only for showcasing the editing skills of the individual.

Starring: Sunny Deol, Varun Dhawan, Diljit Dosanjh, Ahan Shetty
Directed by: Anurag Singh
Featuring the iconic "Sandese Aate Hai 2.0" by Sonu Nigam & Arijit Singh

Release Date: 22 January 2026 (Just before Republic Day)
Genre: Patriotic War Drama | Action | Emotional Blockbuster

About Border 2:
25 years after the legendary Border (1997), the saga continues! Border 2 tells the untold stories of bravery and sacrifice during India‚Äôs wartime glory, bringing back Sunny Deol‚Äôs unforgettable soldier avatar alongside a powerful new generation of heroes.

Tell us in the comments ‚Äì Which moment from the original Border still gives you goosebumps?

#Border2 #Border2Trailer #SunnyDeol #VarunDhawan #DiljitDosanjh #Bollywood #WarFilm #PatrioticMovie #RepublicDay2026 #SandeseAateHai2

Follow us on social media for the latest news:
- Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/moviecruzzer/
- X handle: https://x.com/moviecruzzer

For business inquiries: moviecruzzerinfo@gmail.com

‚ùØ‚ùØ In this channel I'm creating Mashup / Fan-made / Concept trailer videos, involve collecting multiple pieces of film footage from one or multiple movies and editing them to create a new trailer. Trailer mashups are often created for a movie that does not exist now or to change the genre of an existing film. These are derivative works and as such, may find protection from copyright claims under the doctrine of fair use. The trailer mashups are not only a user-generated form of digital creativity but a way to create anticipation for future releases, working in tandem with current movie trailers. Movie trailers are designed to give minimal plot detail and to create hype and anticipation. Fan-made trailer mashups allow the audience to perform their own cinematic spin on current movie footage. This allows the trailer to focus on a specific actor or portion of the film. It could even change the plot or genre of the film entirely.

Softwares used : Adobe Premiere Pro, After Effects & Photoshop.
Cutz & Design: Movie Cruzzer & team

snippet.title: Minecraft Speedrunner Swap VS 2 Hunters
snippet.description:
This was crazy intense. Manhunt, but with a twist.

This video, I teamed up with my rival, Daquavis, in a new #MinecraftManhunt challenge. We have to speedrun and beat Minecraft against two hunters, but we swap who is playing every minute! It was hilarious and super intense.

Follow my socials:
‚ûΩ Twitter - @dreamwastaken
‚ûΩ Instagram - @dreamwastaken
‚ûΩ Snapchat - @dreampublic


In this challenge Daquavis and I essentially are one player. We share an inventory, health, position, and basically everything else. The idea is that we are swapping who has control of one player. When we are swapped out, we don't know what is happening at all. We see a black screen and hear nothing.

This video was inspired by a similar challenge, without hunters, posted here: https://youtu.be/WU5etmP0h0Y?si=kzoxiP04YnD74_Ni

This was played on Minecraft 1.21.8, and is a custom coded challenge. There were a few bugs that we plan to iron out before we try something like this again!

300,000 likes for me to try this challenge with someone else!


George: @GeorgeNotFound 
Sapnap: @Sapnap 
Daquavis: @DaquavisMC 

Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/DreamWasTaken

‚ú® Achyutam Keshavam ‚Äì A Devotional Krishna Bhajan ‚ú®
 "Achyutam Keshavam" is a timeless and soul-soothing bhajan dedicated to Lord Krishna, praising their divine names, virtues, and forms. The bhajan beautifully recites various names of the Lord - Achyuta, Keshava, Narayana, and more - each carrying deep spiritual meaning.
Singing this bhajan is believed to purify the heart, remove sorrows, and bring the blessings of the Supreme Lord. It reminds devotees to surrender completely to God, trusting His eternal protection and grace.


üå∏ Chant ‚ÄúAchyutam Keshavam‚Äù with devotion and invite divine bliss into your life.

lava_hunter03 is playing his Minecraft world as normal, but than one day everything changes. He suddenly becomes inactive on all of his accounts, and goes silent. After investigating, we discover some horrifying secrets linked to the player.

This is a series called Minecraft ARG where I solve Minecraft mysteries. Not Secret Minecraft things or Minecraft lore (like Game Theory) or Escape Rooms, but a research based series dedicated to solving Minecraft arg channels.
